bio: Rakia is a Google Developer Expert in Angular, WTM Ambassador, and a content creator. She has an experience of 17 years as a software engineer during which she has worked with many technologies and frameworks. She is active on Medium (150+ articles, 700K+ views, https://rakiabensassi.medium.com/), and YouTube: 55K+ views: https://www.youtube.com/@tekforge. She has also a Udemy video course (25K+ students) about Web Performance & Memory Leaks: https://www.udemy.com/course/identify-and-fix-javascript-memory-leaks
